# Commit Context First

- At the start of work, read `.cursor/context/last-commit.md` when it exists.
- Treat it as the latest repo state signal after the most recent commit.

# Writing Constraints

- Do not use em dash characters.
- Do not use arrow symbols in prose.
- Prefer plain, direct sentences.
